      "tag_name": "v0.4.0",
      "name": "v0.4.0",
      "body": "## Quick Install (recommended)\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -fsSL https://zigcli.liujiacai.net/install.sh | sh\r\n```\r\nThere are some options to configure this script, see: https://zigcli.liujiacai.net/install/\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* feat: add gitignore module by @jiacai2050 in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/53\r\n* Fix a integer overflow error caused by the small zstd decompression buffer size by @qilme in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/54\r\n* fix: treat slash as invalid rules by @jiacai2050 in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/55\r\n* Add newline to printVersion by @LDprg in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/56\r\n* feat(gitignore): remove libc fnmatch dependency and implement pure Zig glob by @jiacai2050 in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/59\r\n* feat(gitignore): Support recursive .gitignore filtering in tree/loc by @jiacai2050 in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/61\r\n* refactor(simargs): improve naming consistency for internal types by @jiacai2050 in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/62\r\n* pretty-table: add Cell struct with per-cell styling and horizontal span by @Copilot in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/63\r\n* Add cowsay command by @Copilot in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/65\r\n* Add `progress` binary: port of https://github.com/Xfennec/progress (Linux + macOS) by @Copilot in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/66\r\n* Add fastfetch binary: system information fetcher by @Copilot in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/69\r\n* feat: fastfetch support color by @jiacai2050 in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/71\r\n* refactor(bin): rename binary to zfetch and modularize by @jiacai2050 in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/72\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @qilme made their first contribution in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/54\r\n* @LDprg made their first contribution in https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/pull/56\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/jiacai2050/zigcli/compare/v0.3.0...v0.4.0",
